definition: to keep/to contain/to suck (keep in your mouth without chewing)

sentences.english: The fossils in the contents of phosphorus are more than 46 times rock.
sentences.chinese: 化石中的含磷量为围岩的46倍以上。

sentences.english: The qualities for both phosphate and phosphate free detergents are analyzed here.
sentences.chinese: 对我国生产含磷与无磷洗衣粉的质量进行了分析。

sentences.english: There are many phosphoric stones on the hill.
sentences.chinese: 那座山上有很多含磷的石头。

sentences.english: In this paper, we studied two kinds of phosphorus heterocycle.
sentences.chinese: 本论文中，我们研究了两类不同的含磷杂环化合物。

sentences.english: Warming and nitrogen deposition had significantly effect on phosphorus content of litter.
sentences.chinese: 增温和施氮对羊草和芦苇凋落物含磷量影响均显著。

sentences.english: Glufosinate is a phosphorus containing amino acid.
sentences.chinese: 草铵膦本身就是一种含磷的氨基酸。

sentences.english: In this paper, the treatment of wastewater containing Phosphorus with porous sponge iron is studied.
sentences.chinese: 研究了金属多孔滤料海绵铁处理含磷废水的各项性能。

sentences.english: The active ingredient in Coke is phosphoric acid.
sentences.chinese: 可乐中的活跃成份就是含磷的酸性物质。

sentences.english: The inner anode includes insoluble carbon and phosphorous-copper bar.
sentences.chinese: 内阳极有两种材质，分别为不溶性碳精棒和含磷铜棒。

sentences.english: Some manufacturer use those who endanger health to contain phosphorous gesso even.
sentences.chinese: 有的厂家甚至使用危害健康的含磷石膏。

sentences.english: The new comprehensive utilization technology of phosphatic dolomite is discussed.
sentences.chinese: 论述了含磷白云石的综合利用新工艺。

sentences.english: New process on phosphorus curing agents of epoxy resin are reviewed.
sentences.chinese: 综述了含磷环氧树脂固化剂研究的新进展。
